<p>
<lb n="1"/>śrī sakavariśa 998 naḷa sa<note n="362-1">After the9 there is a dot and after 8 a stroke, which evidently are to be ignored.</note>
<lb n="2" break="no"/>ṁvatsarada saṁkrāṁti Ādivaradaṁ
<lb n="3" break="no"/>du dēvēṁdrapaṁḍitara siśyara
<lb n="4" break="no"/>ppa saṁkarakōṭi kalidēvasvāmi
<lb n="5" break="no"/>ge koruvari yapattu kaṁ
<lb n="6" break="no"/>bha(ṁ)kka Eraḍu daravaṁdakkaṁ
<lb n="7"/>koṭṭa gadyāṇa mūvattu
<lb n="8"/>ruvari kētōjana besa
<lb n="9"/>maṁgaḷa mahā śrī śrī
</p>

